casebody.data:
Randall Lee CONRAD
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 355P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 23, 2004. Randall Lee Conrad, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Plaintiff on the 16th day of July 2004 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Stokes County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 23rd day of July 2004."
